              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "The Targets were self-supporting foils 99.66% Zn-64",
                "enriched isotope (0.21% ZN-66 CONTAMINATION) with",
                "thicknesses of 2.0 and 0.81 Mg/Cm**2.",
