              "coded_information": [
                "STRUC"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " Transitions System in Ga-64.",
                "Q-Value For (P,N) Reaction on Zn-64 was determined.",
                "Angular Distributions for some neutron group were",
                "measured too. But the Results are presented on very",
                "small figures.  Therefore unabmiguous reading of the",
                "Data is impossible.",
                "Half-Life of 128.1-KeV Level was measured. (6.9+/-0.7",
